long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Getlatests is a Chrome extension designed to bring you the latest news automatically and quickly. 
The main feature of Getlatests is the ability to automatically monitor and update random article lists from getlatests. This is done through the fetchFeed function, a function designed to continuously fetch data from a website's RSS feed and store them in an array. When users open the widget's popup, they can immediately see the latest articles without having to visit the website directly.

The app is built by GetLastest where you can find brilliant custom Hawaiian shirts to nostalgic vintage t-shirts and personalized embroidered sweatshirts.
